1
00:01:33,590 --> 00:01:36,539
[Eternal Brotherhood 2]

2
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:44,720
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:51,280
On the vast land of Xichuan,

4
00:01:51,770 --> 00:01:54,720
various family forces
are deeply intertwined.

5
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:57,430
Among them, Zichuan and the North Clan

6
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,950
have been at war for years,

7
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,550
evenly matched in strength.

8
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:04,200
Zichuan Xiu, an orphan,

9
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:06,150
was adopted from a young age
by Zichuan Yuanxing,

10
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:08,210
the Chieftain of the Zichuan family.

11
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:10,840
He grew up alongside
the family's heiress, Zichuan Ning,

12
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,360
and formed a deep childhood bond with her.

13
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:16,280
He also became sworn brothers
with Di Lin, the Minister

14
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,710
of Military and Legal Affairs,
and Si Yilin,

15
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:20,280
commander of the Palace Guards.

16
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,710
The three of them swore to protect

17
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,680
the peace of Zichuan together.

18
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,280
After being exiled to
the distant frontier of Yuanzhou

19
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,190
for many years, Zichuan Xiu

20
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:32,430
achieved great military success

21
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:34,310
and returned triumphantly
to the Imperial Capital,

22
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:37,800
only to find that the clan
was already riddled with crisis.

23
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:41,190
Internally, Yang Minghua
harbored grand ambitions

24
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,520
and plotted treachery.

25
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,400
Externally, the North Clan stirred unrest

26
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,200
at the borders, ready to invade.

27
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:50,590
Zichuan Xiu joined forces
with Di Lin and Si Yilin

28
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:53,470
to quell Yang Minghua's rebellion,

29
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:56,310
successfully defending
the Imperial Capital.

30
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:58,030
However, they were unable to

31
00:02:58,030 --> 00:03:00,400
halt the rising conflict at the frontier.

32
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:04,030
Yang Minghua's trusted general, Lei Hong,

33
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,750
colluded with the North Clan

34
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:09,590
and launched a full-scale invasion
against Zichuan,

35
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:12,800
capturing the last line of defense,

36
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,750
Payi City.

37
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,590
Zichuan Xiu and Si Yilin

38
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:19,840
rushed to Payi,

39
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,400
recaptured the city
through a clever strategy,

40
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,560
and seriously wounded the enemy general,

41
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,310
dealing a major blow to the North Clan.

42
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,870
However,

43
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:30,560
the North Clan sent Lei Hong again

44
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,000
to lead a massive army to attack Payi.

45
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:35,000
Food was scarce in the city,

46
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,930
and the casualties were mounting.

47
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,630
Zichuan Xiu and Si Yilin,

48
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,630
with only a handful of troops,

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,810
were forced into a desperate defense.

50
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:46,360
At this critical moment,
Di Lin, who was guarding the capital,

51
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:49,030
was ordered to lead
reinforcements to Payi.

52
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,890
The three brothers were finally reunited

53
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:54,590
and resolved to fight side by side

54
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,000
to defend Zichuan to the end.

55
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,820
You're just walking right into a trap.

56
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,690
Didn't you just say that

57
00:04:00,690 --> 00:04:02,950
their actions were incredibly foolish?

58
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,470
That's right.

59
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,270
Those two are the biggest fools.

60
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,820
And I'm the third fool.

61
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:31,050
My Lady, there's an official
requesting an audience.

62
00:04:31,050 --> 00:04:33,700
He doesn't look familiar.

63
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,630
Could he be some newly appointed official

64
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:37,360
trying to curry favor with you?

65
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:39,810
His name is Ma Wei.

66
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:41,180
I'll go ask him to leave.

67
00:04:42,730 --> 00:04:44,170
He's not just some random new official.

68
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:46,550
[Zichuan Ning]

69
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:47,930
He's the youngest advisor
of the Three Central Offices.

70
00:04:47,930 --> 00:04:49,780
I've sent several people to Yuanzhou

71
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:51,370
to search for Lord Xiu's whereabouts.

72
00:04:51,370 --> 00:04:52,780
Initially, there were no results,

73
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:53,909
but just yesterday,

74
00:04:54,050 --> 00:04:56,580
my men finally located
Xiu Battalion's camp.

75
00:04:56,810 --> 00:04:58,220
By the time we arrived at the camp,

76
00:04:58,220 --> 00:05:01,420
it was already deserted.
Lord Xiu was nowhere to be found.

77
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,220
However, upon inspection,

78
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,220
[Ma Wei, Member of Three Central Offices]

79
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,960
the camp showed
no signs of being attacked.

80
00:05:06,610 --> 00:05:10,010
It's clear that the soldiers
retreated in an orderly manner.

81
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:11,170
I believe

82
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,040
Lord Xiu was perfectly fine when he left.

83
00:05:15,170 --> 00:05:17,880
If Lord Xiu left the camp safely,

84
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,530
[Mei]

85
00:05:18,290 --> 00:05:21,150
then he might already
be on his way back with troops.

86
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:23,980
That's great news, Your Highness.

87
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:28,700
That guy always seems to
run faster than anyone,

88
00:05:29,740 --> 00:05:30,710
but he would never

89
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:32,070
abandon Si Yilin alone.

90
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:39,550
He must have received some information

91
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:42,040
and left the camp to offer support.

92
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:43,930
In that case,

93
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,630
with Lord Xiu's assistance,

94
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:47,990
Lord Si Yilin will be

95
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:49,659
greatly empowered.

96
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:55,460
It's just that this time,
the North Clan has overwhelming forces.

97
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:56,900
I fear that even with
the two of them joining forces,

98
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:59,430
they still won't be able to
hold their ground.

99
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:07,250
But if they

100
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:08,460
are really together,

101
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,380
they can support each other.

102
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:18,070
Once the frontline battle begins,

103
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:20,600
word will surely reach
the Imperial Capital.

104
00:06:20,770 --> 00:06:22,830
And so far, there has been no bad news.

105
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:25,770
It means that at least
they are safe for now.

106
00:06:26,990 --> 00:06:28,340
Please rest assured, Your Highness.

107
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:29,610
I will continue searching

108
00:06:29,610 --> 00:06:32,140
for Lord Xiu and Lord Si Yilin's
whereabouts.

109
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,760
If I receive any news,
I will report it at once.

110
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:43,950
Then I thank you in advance, Lord Ma Wei.

111
00:06:47,610 --> 00:06:50,270
Looks like Lord Chieftain
was overthinking it.

112
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:52,340
What is it?

113
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,290
Lord Chieftain was worried

114
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,460
that this kind of news

115
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,920
would make Your Highness
even more anxious.

116
00:07:01,210 --> 00:07:03,890
But I had already promised Your Highness,

117
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:05,200
so I couldn't lie.

118
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:06,900
I could only tell the truth.

119
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:08,730
I didn't expect that

120
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:11,350
Your Highness wouldn't
lose composure at all.

121
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:17,510
That's because I've been toughened

122
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,610
by Zichuan Xiu.

123
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:22,340
When he was away in Yuanzhou
for seven years,

124
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,570
he was always

125
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,540
getting lost in the desert,

126
00:07:26,210 --> 00:07:28,810
or his whole army was caught
in fierce battles.

127
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,630
This time, with Si Yilin by his side,

128
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:33,090
I'm actually more at ease.

129
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:36,870
Your Highness truly has

130
00:07:37,409 --> 00:07:39,070
a deep affection for Lord Xiu.

131
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:51,700
What?

132
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:55,070
Fearing that Your Highness might worry,

133
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,909
I specially arranged a place
for you to relax.

134
00:07:56,909 --> 00:07:57,780
But now it seems

135
00:07:58,100 --> 00:07:59,830
I was worrying unnecessarily.

136
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:02,560
Never mind.

137
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:05,980
Let's postpone the visit.

138
00:08:06,370 --> 00:08:07,630
I'll take my leave now.

139
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:10,320
If any further news
from the front lines comes,

140
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:12,650
I will immediately inform Your Highness.

141
00:08:16,610 --> 00:08:18,010
Lord Ma Wei, please wait.

142
00:08:23,490 --> 00:08:24,930
I wonder what kind of arrangements

143
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:26,240
you have already made.

144
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:29,420
I found a few fine horses

145
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:33,110
and was hoping Your Highness
could try them out with me.

146
00:08:33,169 --> 00:08:35,440
But if today is not a good time...

147
00:08:47,010 --> 00:08:48,840
I once had a beloved horse too,

148
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,930
but it got lost.

149
00:09:00,770 --> 00:09:01,480
Let's go.

150
00:09:02,770 --> 00:09:03,370
After you.

151
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,530
Why do I feel like

152
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,980
I've been here before?

153
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,420
Your Highness,

154
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:17,140
actually, we met once
when we were children.

155
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:17,840
Right here.

156
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:23,260
When you came with
Lord Chieftain back then,

157
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,720
you said this road was beautiful,

158
00:09:26,370 --> 00:09:28,720
but the sunlight was harsh and blinding.

159
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,570
You wished for shade along the way,

160
00:09:31,570 --> 00:09:33,770
so it would be more comfortable to walk.

161
00:09:35,410 --> 00:09:37,200
Then I pleaded with my father

162
00:09:37,410 --> 00:09:39,610
to plant trees on both sides of the road.

163
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,770
Now, even under the blazing sun,

164
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:43,300
it feels cool and pleasant.

165
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,270
I never imagined that,

166
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,390
years later, I'd truly have the chance

167
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,790
to invite you here again.

168
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:54,010
That was just a casual remark
I made as a child.

169
00:09:54,650 --> 00:09:56,650
I never expected you to remember it.

170
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,720
I remember at that time,

171
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,840
I even tumbled off

172
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,770
that big rock.

173
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,930
A little boy helped me up.

174
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:09,840
Was that also you, Lord Ma Wei?

175
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,010
We're about the same age.

176
00:10:13,010 --> 00:10:14,410
Your Highness doesn't need to
be so formal.

177
00:10:14,410 --> 00:10:15,470
Just call me Ma Wei.

178
00:10:21,430 --> 00:10:24,360
Your Highness, why not rest on horseback?

179
00:10:25,170 --> 00:10:25,840
And you?

180
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:29,140
I'll gladly serve as your groom,
Your Highness.

181
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:33,470
Come on.

182
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:42,230
I remember when I was young,

183
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:44,690
I used to love horseback riding with Xiu.

184
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:47,710
Back then, I even asked him to teach me,

185
00:10:48,190 --> 00:10:49,580
but he always refused.

186
00:10:50,690 --> 00:10:52,130
Then we had a race,

187
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:53,190
and I actually won.

188
00:10:55,010 --> 00:10:57,680
Lord Xiu was surely being thoughtful
toward Your Highness.

189
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,900
He must have let you win,

190
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,160
just to make you happy.

191
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:04,480
Yes, back then I truly believed

192
00:11:04,810 --> 00:11:06,960
I won because I was better than him.

193
00:11:07,250 --> 00:11:08,680
Only later did I realize

194
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,370
he actually went easy on me.

195
00:11:11,330 --> 00:11:12,560
When Lord Xiu returns,

196
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,720
I want to challenge him too.

197
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:21,180
Wh-What's wrong?

198
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:22,050
Did you know?

199
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,380
The Xiu Battalion and Palace Guards

200
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:25,180
have less than

201
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,930
ten days of supplies.

202
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:28,960
If we keep getting trapped here,

203
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,420
we'll all starve to death.

204
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:31,480
I don't believe

205
00:11:31,810 --> 00:11:33,130
those North Clan soldiers

206
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:34,130
could completely

207
00:11:34,130 --> 00:11:35,250
seal off Payi City,

208
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,010
without leaving a single gap.

209
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:38,960
Yeah, if we can just find a way out,
we could escape.

210
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,440
That's right.

211
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,930
So you want to be deserters, huh?

212
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:42,170
Who said anything about running away?

213
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:43,030
Think about it.

214
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:43,930
Right now, our commanders

215
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:46,050
are desperately trying
to figure things out.

216
00:11:46,050 --> 00:11:47,810
If we can find a way out

217
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:49,020
and bring back food,

218
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:50,650
we'd be heroes.

219
00:11:50,850 --> 00:11:52,910
Then, not only would we get rewarded,

220
00:11:53,050 --> 00:11:54,320
but Lord Xiu

221
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,130
might even promote us to Lieutenants.

222
00:11:56,130 --> 00:11:57,460
Are you sure about this?

223
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:59,880
I already got word from the sentries.

224
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:02,820
[Li Nong, Maocai, Ze]

225
00:12:00,810 --> 00:12:03,440
The fortifications outside the East Gate
are already damaged.

226
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:06,250
It must be because the North Clan soldiers
cut corners before.

227
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:09,410
Lately, there's been no sign
of them around.

228
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,490
This is the perfect chance.

229
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,390
Most importantly, Maocai,

230
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,840
there are plenty of forests
outside the East Gate.

231
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:19,290
This season, it's like
a kitchen out there.

232
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,960
Wild game is everywhere.

233
00:12:32,010 --> 00:12:33,250
Bad news, Lord Xiu!

234
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,920
There are deserters
at the East Gate of Payi City!

235
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,380
They injured our sentries

236
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,680
and escaped the city!

237
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,930
Which unit are they from?

238
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:40,590
They're...

239
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,670
They're from the Xiu Battalion.

240
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,250
[Zichuan Xiu]

241
00:13:06,930 --> 00:13:08,600
Ah, the smell of nature!

242
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:16,520
Keep it down, or you'll attract wolves.

243
00:13:20,250 --> 00:13:22,440
I can't believe we made it out so easily.

244
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,460
Not only is no one chasing us,

245
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:25,080
but there's not even
a single North Clan scout in sight.

246
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,010
I told you,

247
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:27,510
there's no way those North Clan soldiers

248
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:29,200
could've completely surrounded

249
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,330
a big city like Payi.

250
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,960
Even if they did,

251
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,360
with our skills,

252
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:35,460
what could possibly stop us?

253
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:42,800
Wait!

254
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,440
Stay alert.

255
00:14:14,410 --> 00:14:15,100
Chief.

256
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:17,200
No more talk. Hurry back with me.

257
00:14:17,350 --> 00:14:18,040
Be careful. There could be ambushes.

258
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,170
Chief, listen to me.

259
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:21,360
There aren't any North Clan soldiers
on this road at all.

260
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,020
We've already found a way out.

261
00:14:23,290 --> 00:14:24,050
You left the city without permission

262
00:14:24,050 --> 00:14:25,560
and were mistaken for deserters
by the Palace Guards.

263
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:25,650
[Baichuan]

264
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,230
Lord Xiu risked his life

265
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:28,040
to come find you.

266
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,440
If something went wrong,
we'd all be doomed.

267
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,080
Now move!

268
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:32,230
We weren't trying to desert!

269
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:34,160
Being trapped in the city
is just waiting to die!

270
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,920
We'd rather risk it outside!

271
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:38,110
You really think the North Clan
is that dumb?

