552
00:29:35,990 --> 00:29:37,990
that allows for both advance and retreat

553
00:29:37,990 --> 00:29:40,510
and can be equipped with
fire-starting devices at any time.

554
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:43,240
Payi is now surrounded
like a sealed iron bucket.

555
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:46,330
No one inside could escape
even if they had wings.

556
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,530
Meticulous indeed.

557
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:49,920
There will be a strong wind today.

558
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,030
It's the best time

559
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,930
to use the wind for a fire assault.

560
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:54,960
If we had arrived an hour later,

561
00:29:55,220 --> 00:29:56,230
there'd be no way

562
00:29:56,260 --> 00:29:57,460
to get into Payi.

563
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:58,730
So, My Lord,

564
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:01,390
should we sneak attack
the enemy camp next,

565
00:30:01,390 --> 00:30:03,640
or join forces with Payi
for a pincer attack?

566
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,990
The gap between our forces
and the enemy's is too big.

567
00:30:04,990 --> 00:30:06,920
Taking the initiative to attack
would be like throwing eggs at a rock.

568
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,250
We must not be reckless.

569
00:30:08,260 --> 00:30:10,270
What if they turn around and attack us?

570
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:10,710
Wouldn't we be...

571
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:12,270
I know Yun Qianxue pretty well.

572
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:13,760
His strength is his meticulousness,

573
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:14,890
but that's also his weakness.

574
00:30:14,890 --> 00:30:16,260
He's too meticulous.

575
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,990
I actually hope

576
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,170
he hesitates for a bit longer.

577
00:30:20,780 --> 00:30:22,060
We need time too.

578
00:30:29,740 --> 00:30:30,870
Are those vultures?

579
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:33,290
They're here waiting for the dead?

580
00:30:34,990 --> 00:30:38,340
With so many battles,
the casualties keep piling up.

581
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:41,400
This clash between the two clans

582
00:30:42,450 --> 00:30:45,180
has left countless
without even a proper burial.

583
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:49,170
They fell in battle,
yet their names are forgotten.

584
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:53,670
Only they are witnessing

585
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:58,560
and honoring the tragedy
of these chaotic days.

586
00:31:01,550 --> 00:31:03,480
You're truly benevolent, My Lord.

587
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:07,030
It's not about kindness or generosity

588
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:09,090
but for the sake of the common people.

589
00:31:09,330 --> 00:31:11,460
Only with peace can the people thrive.

590
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:14,680
The Executioner on the Battlefield
has arrived.

591
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:16,340
When the final assault comes,

592
00:31:16,490 --> 00:31:18,550
there will be fierce fighting again,

593
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:21,920
and many more from both the North Clan

594
00:31:21,950 --> 00:31:23,710
and Zichuan will fall.

595
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:28,320
Human desires never lessen,
and wars never end.

596
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:30,600
When will the attrition

597
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:33,520
between the two clans ever end?

598
00:31:40,090 --> 00:31:41,050
My brothers,

599
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:45,450
we, the Palace Guards
and the Xiu Battalion,

600
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:49,410
have been ordered to campaign
against the North Clan in the east.

601
00:31:49,410 --> 00:31:51,810
We've been through so much
on this journey.

602
00:31:52,230 --> 00:31:53,600
Now, outside Payi City,

603
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:55,960
the North Clan is eyeing us covetously.

604
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:58,920
Inside Payi City, we're short on supplies.

605
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:02,540
I know everyone has suffered a lot.

606
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,990
I also know everyone is hungry.

607
00:32:06,330 --> 00:32:08,590
I hope you all can
hold on a little longer.

608
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:20,030
Gentlemen, the famous military strategist,

609
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:23,140
Master Zuo Jiaming, once said that

610
00:32:25,910 --> 00:32:30,120
the most important factor
in war is persistence.

611
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:31,990
Beyond persistence,

612
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:34,790
there's even more persistence.

613
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:37,350
Victory comes from persistence.

614
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:42,030
To help everyone keep going,

615
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:44,080
we have specially prepared

616
00:32:44,230 --> 00:32:46,960
some delicious food

617
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:49,600
to replenish your strength.

618
00:32:49,890 --> 00:32:51,740
Bravo!

619
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:54,230
Bravo!

620
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:55,880
Bravo!

621
00:33:33,150 --> 00:33:33,680
Go ahead.

622
00:33:38,280 --> 00:33:39,740
Come on, folks in the back!

623
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:41,360
It smells so good.

624
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:42,760
Don't push, one at a time!

625
00:33:43,730 --> 00:33:45,060
Lord Wen He, have some.

626
00:33:45,090 --> 00:33:45,960
It's my turn!

627
00:33:47,120 --> 00:33:47,710
Come on.

628
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,320
Serve me a bowl first.

629
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:50,770
Hurry!

630
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:52,000
Is it enough?

631
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,160
Hurry up!

632
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,070
Come on, next.

633
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:56,460
It smells so good.

634
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,220
Have some.

635
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,700
I don't want to eat.

636
00:34:00,310 --> 00:34:01,160
It smells so good! Hurry!

637
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:01,620
My Lord.

638
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,380
There's enough for everyone.

639
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,310
My Lord,

640
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:07,530
I know you don't want to eat.

641
00:34:07,530 --> 00:34:08,830
Do you think I want to?

642
00:34:09,210 --> 00:34:10,670
All our brothers are here.

643
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:13,560
You have to set an example.

644
00:34:13,730 --> 00:34:14,460
Here, yours.

645
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:33,550
It's salty.

646
00:34:34,989 --> 00:34:36,250
It's the taste of salt.

647
00:34:38,830 --> 00:34:40,090
Since we entered Payi,

648
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,679
this is the first time I've tasted salt.

649
00:34:44,489 --> 00:34:47,330
Everyone, eat and drink up!

650
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:50,320
Alright!

651
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,630
Alright!

652
00:34:53,699 --> 00:34:55,889
There's salt and meat,

653
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:58,420
all to help restore strength.

654
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,120
Everyone, have some.

655
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:03,150
Alright!

656
00:35:12,270 --> 00:35:15,830
Second Brother, don't be so dejected.

657
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:19,170
This isn't how
the Tiger of Zichuan should look.

658
00:35:20,290 --> 00:35:22,290
If I were truly the Tiger of Zichuan,

659
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,440
I'd rather strip the bones and flesh

660
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:28,360
to feed them.

661
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:35,240
Back when I was in Hengchuan,

662
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:38,380
I personally killed

663
00:35:39,430 --> 00:35:42,030
a warhorse that had
followed me for five years.

664
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:44,720
It was our failure.

665
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:53,800
Second Brother, just imagine:

666
00:35:54,610 --> 00:35:56,880
If horses were our masters,

667
00:35:57,880 --> 00:36:00,590
and they were struggling
to defend Payi City,

668
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,150
what would you do?

669
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:05,310
Remember what you said just now?

670
00:36:05,470 --> 00:36:07,200
Stripping the bones and flesh?

671
00:36:13,530 --> 00:36:15,390
I underestimated our warhorses.

672
00:36:15,770 --> 00:36:16,900
They're all heroes.

673
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:22,880
I have an idea.

674
00:36:24,130 --> 00:36:28,250
Second Brother,
given the current situation,

675
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:29,850
to break the deadlock,

676
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:32,650
it might have to be a fight to the death.

677
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:33,440
I bet

678
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,990
you can't think of a better plan.

679
00:36:37,220 --> 00:36:38,060
That's right.

680
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,970
It's not a good idea.

681
00:36:43,110 --> 00:36:44,560
I'll lead 5,000 cavalry

682
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:46,250
to fight against Yun Qianxue.

683
00:36:46,470 --> 00:36:47,990
That will tear open a gap.

684
00:36:48,510 --> 00:36:52,040
You and the Xiu Battalion
take the civilians and get out of here.

685
00:36:53,730 --> 00:36:57,480
Second Brother,
then you and those 5,000 soldiers

686
00:36:57,800 --> 00:36:58,880
will surely die.

687
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:06,500
This is the best plan
I could come up with.

688
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:14,120
Certainly, but it's not the best.

689
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,950
Yes, if he were here,

690
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,660
he'd definitely come.

691
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,990
He won't abandon us.

692
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:29,880
Your bond of brotherhood runs deep.

693
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,550
Today, I'll show you

694
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,720
the power of the Bald King.

695
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:42,840
Chief.

696
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:43,990
Chief.

697
00:37:44,140 --> 00:37:44,870
Big Brother,

698
00:37:45,250 --> 00:37:46,960
you're a bit late today.

699
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:48,840
We've been bullied for quite a while.

700
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:51,090
Big Brother, how did you know
we were here?

701
00:37:51,090 --> 00:37:52,490
What's so strange about that?

702
00:37:52,490 --> 00:37:54,640
Big Brother always shows up just in time.

703
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:55,600
It's no time

704
00:37:55,810 --> 00:37:57,070
to talk about that now.

705
00:37:57,720 --> 00:38:00,360
Can't you two cause me less trouble?

706
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:01,370
Ask Xiu.

707
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,810
It's all because of
Second Brother, that fool.

708
00:38:02,810 --> 00:38:03,820
He's so easily provoked.

709
00:38:03,820 --> 00:38:05,010
You're a fool too.

710
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:06,220
Why did you just go along with him?

711
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:07,280
-And you?
-And you?

712
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:10,320
Knowing you two,

713
00:38:10,720 --> 00:38:12,470
I'm the biggest fool of all.

714
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:13,670
Charge!

715
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,340
If Big Brother knew

716
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:29,050
about our situation in Payi City,

717
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,650
he would definitely come.

718
00:38:31,990 --> 00:38:33,460
But the North Clan soldiers

719
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:35,590
have the entire Payi City surrounded.

720
00:38:35,590 --> 00:38:36,840
How can he get in?

721
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:40,330
This isn't the military academy
in Yuanzhou.

722
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:44,280
For him, it's all simple.

723
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:47,470
My Lord, a sentry reports:

724
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,690
The North Clan camp
has a large number of reinforcements.

725
00:38:49,690 --> 00:38:50,890
All troops, on alert!

726
00:38:50,990 --> 00:38:51,590
Yes, sir!

727
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:54,910
Second Brother, do you remember

728
00:38:55,390 --> 00:38:58,320
we confiscated
some North Clan soldiers' uniforms?

729
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:03,170
Go, take all the confiscated
North Clan uniforms

730
00:39:03,170 --> 00:39:04,110
and give them to Xiu.

731
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:04,640
Yes, sir.

732
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,260
Safety is the top priority

733
00:39:10,610 --> 00:39:12,140
when entering enemy camps.

734
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,860
Don't worry, Second Brother.

735
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,660
Stealing and slipping away—

736
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:20,440
that's what I'm best at.

737
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:39,680
Oh meat, I've missed you so much!

738
00:39:40,130 --> 00:39:42,540
Let me take you home, alright? Okay.

739
00:39:56,460 --> 00:39:58,680
Why are you still standing here? Let's go!

740
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:00,790
We hadn't heard that
the Divine Emperor was coming.

741
00:40:00,790 --> 00:40:01,710
Why so sudden?

742
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:04,830
His Majesty must want to
personally oversee the battle,

743
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:06,270
and take down Zichuan in one fell swoop.

744
00:40:06,270 --> 00:40:07,320
I'm not one to talk, but

745
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:09,200
General Yun is way too cautious.

746
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:11,230
If I had this many troops,

747
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:13,550
I would have taken down
three Payis by now.

748
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,280
Keep your voice down. Let's go.

749
00:40:40,620 --> 00:40:43,270
Yun, with Father arriving,

750
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:46,520
he'll probably blame us for
not making any progress.

751
00:40:46,870 --> 00:40:47,980
But I see

752
00:40:48,990 --> 00:40:50,840
a bit of expectation in your eyes.

753
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:51,700
Your Highness,

754
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:55,400
the reason we're in a stalemate
with the Zichuan army

755
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,360
is all due to Di Lin's interference,

756
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:59,590
which has drained our military strength.

757
00:40:59,590 --> 00:41:01,750
Now that His Majesty has led troops here,

758
00:41:01,750 --> 00:41:03,480
the stalemate might be broken.

759
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:05,020
How can I not expect it?

760
00:41:05,280 --> 00:41:07,670
You only care about war.

761
00:41:07,700 --> 00:41:09,830
You don't understand politics at all.

762
00:41:10,190 --> 00:41:11,190
With Father here,

763
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:13,170
our credit will be taken away.

764
00:41:14,240 --> 00:41:16,040
The Divine Emperor has arrived!

765
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:29,520
When do you plan
to take down the Payi City?

766
00:41:25,330 --> 00:41:28,680
[Divine Emperor of Sairong]

767
00:41:32,030 --> 00:41:33,840
Do you realize how much Payi City

768
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:36,150
means to the North Clan?

769
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,240
-I do.
-I do.

770
00:41:40,700 --> 00:41:42,270
What's the current situation
of the battle?

771
00:41:42,270 --> 00:41:43,980
Payi City has been under siege for days.

772
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:45,870
They've long since run out
of ammunition and food.

773
00:41:45,870 --> 00:41:48,250
We should have taken it down
three days ago,

774
00:41:48,250 --> 00:41:50,690
but Di Lin's forces suddenly appeared.

775
00:41:50,950 --> 00:41:52,420
[Black Veil, Counsellor of North Clan]

776
00:41:51,270 --> 00:41:53,550
We had to split our forces
to deal with them,

777
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:55,470
which delayed our final assault.

778
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:59,640
Is Di Lin really that formidable?

779
00:42:00,540 --> 00:42:01,800
Not worth mentioning.

780
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:05,180
But General Yun has always been cautious
in his military operations,

781
00:42:05,180 --> 00:42:08,440
not wanting our soldiers
to make unnecessary sacrifices.

782
00:42:09,570 --> 00:42:13,180
Yes, but I have crossed swords
with him before.

783
00:42:13,250 --> 00:42:16,210
He's ruthless and tactically brilliant.

784
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,490
He should not be underestimated.

785
00:42:19,720 --> 00:42:20,400
Yun,

786
00:42:21,470 --> 00:42:23,870
you're giving
too much credit to the enemy.

787
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:26,250
Please forgive my bluntness,

788
00:42:26,670 --> 00:42:29,510
but just from Di Lin's troop movements
and patrol patterns,

789
00:42:29,510 --> 00:42:30,550
one can tell

790
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:33,550
he is very skilled in warfare

791
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:35,770
and has a thorough strategic mind.

792
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:39,440
Our army is fortunate to have Yun.

793
00:42:41,870 --> 00:42:42,710
Ka Lan,

794
00:42:45,490 --> 00:42:47,540
you are fortunate as well.

795
00:42:49,630 --> 00:42:50,830
You may all leave now.

796
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:51,920
Yes.

797
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:57,840
Yun, stay.

798
00:43:28,630 --> 00:43:32,540
Yun, if you have any questions,
ask freely.

799
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:34,080
Your Majesty is wise.

800
00:43:35,360 --> 00:43:37,320
May I ask, how many reinforcements

801
00:43:37,340 --> 00:43:39,070
have you brought, Your Majesty?

802
00:43:39,070 --> 00:43:40,730
Not reinforcements exactly.

803
00:43:40,950 --> 00:43:43,410
I've only brought
my 100,000 Royal Escorts.

804
00:43:44,450 --> 00:43:45,850
That's more than enough.

805
00:43:46,480 --> 00:43:49,730
Then I have a small question as well.

806
00:43:51,510 --> 00:43:54,910
When can we take down Payi?

807
00:43:55,110 --> 00:43:55,760
Tomorrow.

808
00:43:56,410 --> 00:43:59,340
Tomorrow, I will spare no effort
to conquer Payi

809
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:01,640
and cut off Si Yilin's head.

810
00:44:07,440 --> 00:44:09,690
Second Brother, have some.

811
00:44:09,710 --> 00:44:10,850
It's delicious.

812
00:44:11,290 --> 00:44:12,890
You went into the enemy camp.

813
00:44:13,050 --> 00:44:14,910
But all you brought back was food?

814
00:44:16,410 --> 00:44:18,150
A great battle is coming.

815
00:44:18,910 --> 00:44:19,470
When?

816
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:20,100
Tomorrow.

817
00:44:24,170 --> 00:44:27,100
Then as we discussed before,
I'll lead the breakout.

818
00:44:27,510 --> 00:44:30,310
When the time comes,
you lead everyone to retreat.

819
00:44:30,550 --> 00:44:33,320
If it were just ordinary
North Clan generals,

820
00:44:33,500 --> 00:44:34,990
maybe we'd still have hope.

821
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:36,630
But within the enemy camp,

822
00:44:37,080 --> 00:44:39,340
not only is General Yun Qianxue present,

823
00:44:39,950 --> 00:44:43,080
the Divine Emperor of Sairong
is also personally overseeing the battle.
